translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  59,17,"Enti wֽ»n mmienu awie־µ ne bonsam gyem, ־µhֽ» na wֽ»ג€™b־µtena. Abֽ»nefoֽ» no akatua ne no"
  59,18,"Mo a moagye adie, monsuro Nyankopֽ»n, na ֽ»kra biara (ntwa nג€™ani) nhw־µ dwuma a (wadi) de ato hֽ» ama (neho) ֽ»kyena; na monsuro Nyankopֽ»n. Nokor־µ s־µ Nyankopֽ»n ne dwuma a modie nyinaa ho amane bֽ» Wura"
  59,19,Na monhw־µ na moankֽ»y־µ s־µ wֽ»n a wֽ»n wer־µ afri Nyankopֽ»n na enti ֶ†maa wֽ»n wer־µ frii wֽ»n ara wֽ»n ho no. Saa nkorֽ»foֽ» no ne abֽ»nefoֽ» no
  59,20,Amanehunu gya no mu foֽ» no ne ֽ»soro aheman no mufoֽ» no nns־µ. ֶ†soro aheman no mufoֽ» no wֽ»ג€™ne nkonimdifoֽ» no
  59,21,"S־µ Yesianee saa Qurג€™aan yi maa bepֽ» a, anka wobehunu s־µ (bepֽ» no) de ahobrase־µ redwidwa ־µnam Nyankopֽ»n ho suro nti. Y־µג€™rey־µ saa mfatoho yi ama nnipa s־µde־µ wֽ»ג€™b־µfa adwen"
  59,22,"ֶ†ne Nyankopֽ»n no a awurade foforֽ» biara nnihֽ» ka Neho no: Kokoam ne Badwam Nimdefoֽ» no, ֶ†ne Ahummֽ»borֽ» Hene no, ֶ†d־µ־µfoֽ» Hene no"
  59,23,"ֶ†no ne Nyankopֽ»n no a awurade foforֽ» biara nni hֽ» ka Neho no; ֶ†hene no a tumi nyinaa hy־µ nensa, Kronkron Hene no, Asomdwi־µ Hene no, Abodweװ‘ Hene no, Ahoban bֽ» Hene no, Otumfoֽ» no a Otumi ade nyinaa y־µ, ֶ†kasa pr־µko a obiara ntumi ne no nni asie, Otumfoֽ» no a Ak־µses־µm fata no. Ahotew Hene ne Nyankopֽ»n, ֶ†so ky־µn s־µ wֽ»ג€™de biribi toto Neho"
  59,24,"ֶ†ne Nyankopֽ»n; ֶ†bֽ»ֽ» Ade־µ no, ֶ†y־µfo no, ֶ†nyomfo no: ֶ†no na abodin papa nyinaa wֽ» no. De־µ ־µwֽ» soro ne asaase so nyinaa bֽ» no abodin; na ֶ†ne Otumfoֽ» no a Otumi ade nyinaa y־µ, ֶ†ne Onyansafoֽ» no"
